# 💧 Water Quality & BPA Prediction

The **Water Quality & BPA Prediction App** is an IoT-enabled system designed for real-time monitoring of water parameters and Bisphenol A (BPA) contamination assessment. It integrates multiple sensors and AI models to provide accurate insights into water safety, helping communities and industries ensure healthier water consumption.

---

## 🌟 Features

- 🧪 **Real-time Water Quality Monitoring**  
  Continuously measures **pH**, **TDS (Total Dissolved Solids)**, and **Turbidity** levels.  

- ⚗️ **BPA Contamination Prediction**  
  Uses machine learning to analyze sensor data and predict potential **BPA concentration risks**.  

- ☁️ **Cloud Integration**  
  Streams sensor data to a cloud dashboard for remote access and long-term tracking.  

- 🚨 **Alerts & Notifications**  
  Generates alerts when unsafe thresholds are detected in any parameter.  

